.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, rock, d&b, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, dutch, american, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, scooter, skateboard
1. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
2. the dutch is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the fan of rock is the person driving the bike##1
5. the american is the fan of folk##1
6. the thai is the person driving the taxi##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the fan of rock and the fan of d&b##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | country     | folk   | d&b      |
| Nationality   | dutch    | thai | american | japanese  |
| Transport     | bike | taxi  | skateboard    | scooter |

