The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, disco, house
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the person drinking coffee is not the fan of house##6
2. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the fan of hip-hop##7
3. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the person drinking tea##7
5. the person drinking tea is the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking milk##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea  | coffee | almond-milk | milk |
| Music-Genre   | house | disco  | electronic  | hip-hop    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | snake  | frog    | goldfish    |

