The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, traveling, gardening, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: german, brazilian, turkish, nigerian
1. the nigerian is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
3. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking sprite is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | milk     | sprite | mirinda        | water       |
| Hobby         | gardening | sudoku    | traveling | baking |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | brazilian  | german    | turkish   |

