4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
7. the designer is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the tram##7
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
9. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
