.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, rock-climbing, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, disaster, sports, documentary
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, turtle, snake
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the person watching drama movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | filmmaking      | rock-climbing | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | disaster | drama  | documentary       |
| Pet           | snake         | turtle       | bird    | goldfish  |

