4. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person eating radish##7
5. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
7. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
9. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
