4. the fan of punk is between the colombian and the owner of the cat##2
5. the canadian is not the fan of country##6
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the owner of the cat is the thai##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
9. the canadian is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the fan of house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | house   | punk        | country        | salsa   |
| Nationality   | thai | canadian   | colombian | polish |
| Pet           | cat  | mouse | goldfish       | lizard |

