.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-14::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, kale, garlic, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, folk, reggae, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, skiing, badminton
1. the fan of folk is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of trance##7
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of folk##7
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
5. the person eating garlic is on the right of the fan of disco##1
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the fan of folk##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
8. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
9. the person who's sport is skiing is not the fan of disco##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | grapes | kiwi | garlic          | kale  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | disco      | folk    | trance   |
| Sport         | golf | cricket  | skiing | badminton |

