5. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
8. the person watching satire movies is not the person who's sport is handball##6
9. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1

