4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
8. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
9. the freelancer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the videographer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | baking | reading   | traveling | woodworking |
| Job           | software-developer     | writer | freelancer   | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific         | action        | zombie  | family   |

