 4. the owner of the turtle is not the person watching action movies##6
 5. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the pony##7
 6. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the accountant is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4     |
